sec = '000001.SZ'
res = ds.query_inst_info(sec, fields=
    'status,selllot,buylot,pricetick,multiplier,product')
assert res.at[sec, 'multiplier'] == 1
assert abs(res.at[sec, 'pricetick'] - 0.01) < 0.01
assert res.at[sec, 'buylot'] == 100
res = ds.query_inst_info('000001.SH')
assert not res.empty
